🧠 AI Chatbot & Translator by Manish Kumar
A Node.js-based AI application featuring:

💬 AI Chatbot — Friendly and intelligent conversations

🌐 Language Translator — Translates text between languages

⚡ Powered by OpenRouter.ai

🔐 Uses environment variables for secure API key access

🚀 Features
Natural language translation

AI chat responses with branding

Express.js backend with CORS support

🔧 Setup
Clone the repo

Install dependencies

Add your OpenRouter API key in .env

Run the server

📬 API Endpoints
/chat — AI chatbot interface

/translate — Translate text between languages

Developed by Manish Kumar. 🤖